## §2. BYpass POINTS (validator lane)

### §2.1 `nattos.sh §40` line 2215

**Before @deferred marker commit 31762c0:**
```sh
VALIDATOR="src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/scanner/file-extension-validator.ts"
if [ ! -f "$VALIDATOR" ]; then
  warn "Validator missing: $VALIDATOR"
  inc_warn "File extension validator missing"
else
  EXT_RESULT=$(npx tsx "$VALIDATOR" "$ROOT" 2>/dev/null)
```

**Bypass:** `npx tsx` direct call vào `.ts` substrate, không qua `.khai` canonical.

**Status:** @deferred marker applied (commit 31762c0 line 2212). Scanner v0.3+ marker-aware → warn không fail.

**Real fix pending:** W1 Nauion Host live → swap `npx tsx "$VALIDATOR"` → `$NAUION_HOST "$CANONICAL"` where `$CANONICAL = "src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/scanner/file-extension-validator.khai"`.

### §2.2 `scripts/nattos-sh-section45.sh` line 16 (MISS từ v1.0 turn 18 — scope-corrected)

Cùng pattern bypass như §2.1:
```sh
VALIDATOR="src/cells/kernel/audit-cell/scanner/file-extension-validator.ts"
if [ -f "$VALIDATOR" ]; then
  RESULT=$(npx tsx "$VALIDATOR" "$ROOT" 2>/dev/null)
```

**Status:** @deferred marker applied (commit 31762c0). Scanner v0.3+ recognize.

**Source of miss:** `nattos.sh §45` refactored thành standalone script `scripts/nattos-sh-section45.sh` — inherited bypass pattern. Turn 18 census em chỉ grep `nattos.sh`, miss directory `scripts/`.

**SCAR-CENSUS-SCOPE-MISS vaccin:** Census scope = `{root}/*.sh + scripts/*.sh + nattos.sh`, không chỉ 1 file primary.

